title: Late goals help Haslett advance to district semis
text: Late goals help Haslett advance to district semis Brian Calloway , Lansing State Journal 12:35 a.m. EDT October 21, 2015 Buy Photo Haslett's Hunter Nash, right, makes a pass against Lansing Eastern's Johnson Irmuva in a Division 2 District soccer game Tuesday in East Lansing.
